#### Key Dates
Create a new key date: omit \`id\`.
\`\`\`json
{
  "version": 1,
  "commandId": "key-date-create-1",
  "createdAt": "2026-03-20T21:45:12.345Z",
  "actor": "claude-delegated",
  "originDeviceId": "device-origin-123",
  "action": "dossier.upsertKeyDate",
